The state of the module. On iOS, this is always going to be
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/STATE\_READY:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}}; only provided for compatibility with Android.

Cancels a pending
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/getProducts:method"}}
{{/crossLink}} call. You will not receive a
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/receivedProducts:event"}}
{{/crossLink}} event if you cancel a product request.

This function is only available on iOS.

This event returns the result of a
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/getProducts:method"}}
{{/crossLink}} call.

Initiates the recovery of recoverable purchases.

The final result of this operation is reported via the
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/receivedPurchases:event"}}
{{/crossLink}} event, which provides an array of all the purchases that
have been recovered.

In addition, you will receive a
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/purchaseUpdate:event"}}
{{/crossLink}} event **for each purchase** that is recovered, as the
recovery progresses. You will want to complete the recovered purchase
as appropriate either via the {{#crossLink "Purchase/complete:method"}}
{{/crossLink}} method by setting the
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/autoCompletePurchase:property"}}
{{/crossLink}} property to <code>true</code>.

This event returns the result of a
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/getPurchases:method"}}
{{/crossLink}} call.

This event provides updates related to
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/startDownloads:method"}}
{{/crossLink}},
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/pauseDownloads:method"}}
{{/crossLink}},
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/resumeDownloads:method"}}
{{/crossLink}}, and
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/cancelDownloads:method"}}
{{/crossLink}} operations.

The current state of the download object.

Possible values are
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/DOWNLOAD\_STATE\_WAITING:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}},
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/DOWNLOAD\_STATE\_ACTIVE:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}},
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/DOWNLOAD\_STATE\_PAUSED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}},
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/DOWNLOAD\_STATE\_FINISHED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}},
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/DOWNLOAD\_STATE\_FAILED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}}, and
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/DOWNLOAD\_STATE\_CANCELED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}},

Only valid if the state is
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/PURCHASE\_STATE\_FAILED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}}.

Only valid if the state is
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/PURCHASE\_STATE\_FAILED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}}.

Receipt of the purchase. Only valid if the state is
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/PURCHASE\_STATE\_PURCHASED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}}.

An array of
{{#crossLink "Download"}}
{{/crossLink}} objects associated with this purchase.

Only valid if the state is
{{#crossLink "InAppProductsModule/PURCHASE\_STATE\_PURCHASED:attribute"}}
{{/crossLink}}.
The {{#crossLink "Download"}}{{/crossLink}} objects stored in this property
must be used to download the content before the purchase is completed;
after that the download objects are no longer usable.
